stimulus:
Ready-Set-Go Task:

  • First, a red circle ("Ready") appears
  • Then, an orange circle ("Set") appears after a delay
  • You must press SPACE after an equal delay
  • Then, a green circle ("Go") appears
  • You'll get feedback for the first 5 trials.

Press any key to begin.
